    * Online Masters Degrees in Psychology
    * Where Can I Work if I Have a Psychology Degree?

This book is a must read for anyone contemplating a major in psychology. Fittingly, the book ends with a chapter titled: &quot;Assessing the Career Outlook for the Psychology Major.&quot;

